{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew that a war was coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember we were coming back from an outing in Buda, to our apartment in Pest, and we were walking and the window was open in the house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the radio announced that the Second World War had begun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And although I was only 11, I was-- I had been a-- student is too strong a word.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a boy, I read a great deal about the First World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The First World War was a very traumatic event for Hungary because Hungary lost huge portions of its territory and its population.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had several friends whose fathers were in the war, and I-- I-- I read a great deal about the war, heard a great deal about the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew that it-- it is horrible and with the new weapons, it will be more horrible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I followed, as a boy, the Spanish Civil War, so I-- I-- I knew about the-- the new power of the-- of the-- of the military airplane and what havoc it can create and the increase in firepower and all that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I-- I did not have a feeling of personal fear.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't, at that time, view myself as being in particular danger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I realized that Hungary will be an ally of Hitler and Mussolini.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, you know, that's a rather interesting point because one of the great joys for me of being in the United States-- and I am patriotic beyond anything you can imagine-- is that when I came to this country, 1947, and then subsequently I became a citizen.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For the first time in my life, I was on the side where I wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
